{"tid":746948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國法院裁定加泰前主席可被引渡回西班牙","createTime":"2018-07-18T03:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T07:01:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ccda6bd10a8386232ae78ed815a18e088c74f9b","tid":746948,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】德國法院裁定，西班牙在法理上有權引渡加泰羅尼亞自治區前主席普伊格蒙特回國受審，但不能以叛亂罪起訴他。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特在法院作出決定後發表講話，形容裁決是一場勝利，證明了馬德里政府指控他叛亂的謊言，又說為爭取加泰地區獨立而被判囚的人是政治犯，馬德里政府應該立即釋放他們，繼續以不存在罪名監禁他們是不公義行為。普伊格蒙特因為推動加泰獨立公投，被馬德里政府指控煽動及叛亂罪，被迫流亡比利時。當局向他發通緝令，他年初在德國邊境被捕。西班牙向德國法院尋求引渡他回國受審。<br />\n<br />\n德國法院周四裁定，西班牙在法理上有權引渡普伊格蒙特回國，但只能以濫用公款罪提出起訴，不能在未有暴力行為下控告他煽動及叛亂罪。西班牙首相桑切斯表示，尊重德國法院裁決。德國檢察部門表示，會盡快就是否引渡作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=312831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D312831&d=t%2FClPAMlwCBvXe8NzHokitZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=f188b4c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D312831&h=bb1d13ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=312831</a>"},{"pid":"b7abab1c3692cfeb6c592008dc3eb6833976dc9d","tid":746948,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc560f21b83da5129d44bdb5a2bc59ee09e490e6","tid":746948,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd135450426c6fa180e05212c8fa2a4df9a4cf9","tid":746948,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"咁撚勁，對外國司法指三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 